"""Test TubeData."""
with requests_mock.Mocker() as mock_req:
    url = lts.API_URL
    mock_req.get(url, text=json.dumps(VALID_RESPONSE))
    test_tube_data = lts.TubeData()
    test_tube_data.update()
    assert test_tube_data.data['Bakerloo'] == {'Description':
        'Nothing to report', 'State': 'Good Service'}
    assert test_tube_data.data['London Overground'] == {'Description':
        'Something', 'State': 'Minor Delays'}
